This paper deals with fine-grained image classification, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves knowledge distillation, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of self-paced learning, which is a technique used in multimedia analysis (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
